<title>USA: US Surgical sues for Circon records.</title>
<headline>US Surgical sues for Circon records.</headline>
<dateline>WILLMINGTON, Del. 1996-09-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>U.S. Surgical Corp and a shareholder of Circon Corp, CEDE &amp; Co., sued Circon in the Delaware Chancery Court on Wednesday as expected.</p>
<p>According to court information papers, the plaintiff have asked for a court order allowing them to see the books and records of Circon Corp in accordance with Delaware law.</p>
<p>On Tuesday U.S. Surgical sued Circon in the same court to block Circon from triggering its poison pill anti-takeover device.</p>
<p>The Wednesday lawsuit seeks expedited action. No other information on the lawsuit is available at this time.</p>
